Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:28.97,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}でも多分　それは多分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:34.38,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}分け合えるものだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:39.16,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}どうにもならなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:44.25,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}困り果てたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:49.47,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}そんな時はすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:55.98,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}話してよ　頼ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:00.03,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}そばにいるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:02.96,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}繋がってるよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.34,0:23:07.89,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}ね　ここで　約束しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:13.67,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}もしも迷い　立ち止まったら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:19.33,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}いつでも隣で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.85,ED-JP_EP24,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}君を照らそう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.30,0:22:18.57,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}總是無能為力
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.57,0:22:23.45,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}令人焦躁不安
Dialogue: 1,0:22:23.78,0:22:28.97,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}但也許 那也許是
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.97,0:22:34.38,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}可以相互分擔之事
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.86,0:22:39.16,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}若是無可奈何
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.16,0:22:44.25,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}一籌莫展
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.15,0:22:49.47,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}這時就馬上
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.47,0:22:55.98,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}向我訴說 來依靠我
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.29,0:23:00.03,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我會伴你身旁
Dialogue: 1,0:23:00.03,0:23:02.96,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}攜手共度風雨
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.34,0:23:07.89,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}來 就在這裡 立下約定
Dialogue: 1,0:23:07.89,0:23:13.67,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}若你陷入迷茫 止步不前
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.67,0:23:19.33,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}我會時刻伴你身旁
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.77,0:23:23.85,ED-CH_EP24,,0,0,70,,{\fad(360,360)\blur2}點亮你的心燈
